--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.1.1 (2017-10-18)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.8.1 (2017-04-16)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.8.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.7.3 (2016-09-03)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.7.2 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.7.1 (2016-05-27)
I: Improve packaging tasks

* Version 0.7.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.6.2 (2016-04-23)
B: Fix OpenSMTPD process name

* Version 0.6.1 (2016-04-15)
I: Improve 'all' 'group' and 'host' options

* Version 0.6.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.5.1 (2016-04-02)
I: Update support information for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.4.2 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.4.1 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-12-24)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.3.3 (2014-12-22)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.3.2 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-08-29)
I: Ensure Ansible role is OS agnostic

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-08-03)
F: Add 'quiesce' (i.e. inactive) state

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-06-23)
B: Add pattern for Postfix service to fix issue on Gentoo

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-05-26)
F: Initial release
